00:00:10.979 --> 00:00:13.213 position:33% line:89% align:start
[REIN grunts]

00:00:15.984 --> 00:00:17.451 position:33% line:89% align:start
[REIN grunts]

00:00:23.992 --> 00:00:24.859 position:30% line:89% align:start
[REIN chuckles]

00:00:24.993 --> 00:00:27.060 position:30% line:89% align:start
[TANIA grunts]

00:00:27.194 --> 00:00:29.764 position:19% line:83% align:start
I hope that extra room
opens up tonight.

00:02:00.722 --> 00:02:02.657 position:41% line:83% align:start
[REIN]
You think I need new equipment?

00:02:02.790 --> 00:02:04.458 position:21% line:83% align:start
Well, yeah. Told you
a bunch of times.

00:02:04.592 --> 00:02:05.560 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KANADE]
You're so much stronger since

00:02:05.693 --> 00:02:07.061 position:7% line:89% align:start
forging your contract with me,

00:02:07.194 --> 00:02:08.863 position:33% line:83% align:start
but you still
have the same gear.

00:02:08.997 --> 00:02:12.533 position:13% line:83% align:start
So, I need equipment that's
better suited for my power.

00:02:12.667 --> 00:02:13.701 position:41% line:89% align:start
Hmm...

00:02:13.835 --> 00:02:15.135 position:41% line:83% align:start
[RUNA]
Whoa!

00:02:15.268 --> 00:02:17.739 position:5% line:83% align:start
Whatever they are seasoning this
soup with is really tasty!

00:02:17.872 --> 00:02:19.974 position:27% line:83% align:start
Now I'm wondering
what their secret is.

00:02:20.108 --> 00:02:21.609 position:41% line:83% align:start
[SORA]
Runa.

00:02:21.743 --> 00:02:24.478 position:13% line:83% align:start
You know better than to be
shouting at the table like this.

00:02:24.612 --> 00:02:26.179 position:16% line:89% align:start
And you're making a mess!

00:02:26.313 --> 00:02:27.515 position:30% line:89% align:start
You know what?

00:02:27.649 --> 00:02:28.750 position:33% line:83% align:start
You're right,
and we do have some money

00:02:28.883 --> 00:02:31.451 position:27% line:83% align:start
in the bank after
that Arios job.

00:02:31.586 --> 00:02:33.353 position:19% line:89% align:start
I'm in, so let's do it!

00:02:33.487 --> 00:02:34.689 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TANIA]
Mm-hm.

00:02:34.822 --> 00:02:35.957 position:27% line:89% align:start
[KANADE chuckles]

00:02:36.090 --> 00:02:38.559 position:21% line:83% align:start
[REIN] It'll help me
protect my team better.

00:02:41.663 --> 00:02:44.065 position:21% line:83% align:start
Not good. There're so
many humans out here!

00:02:44.197 --> 00:02:45.700 position:5% line:89% align:start
If they find out we're fairies,

00:02:45.833 --> 00:02:48.235 position:13% line:83% align:start
who knows what they'll do,
so be on the look out, Sis!

00:02:48.368 --> 00:02:50.404 position:21% line:83% align:start
Yes, well, don't you
worry one bit, Runa.

00:02:50.538 --> 00:02:52.305 position:21% line:83% align:start
Because I swear on my
life, that this time,

00:02:52.439 --> 00:02:55.175 position:10% line:83% align:start
I'll do whatever it takes to
keep you safe and sound!

00:02:55.308 --> 00:02:56.744 position:27% line:89% align:start
Relax, you guys.

00:02:56.878 --> 00:02:59.413 position:19% line:83% align:start
It's not like all of us
humans are bad. I promise.

00:02:59.547 --> 00:03:01.649 position:10% line:89% align:start
I will take you at your word.

00:03:01.783 --> 00:03:03.017 position:38% line:89% align:start
I dunno.

00:03:03.151 --> 00:03:04.686 position:10% line:83% align:start
I'm not sure if I'll ever be
able to get used to this.

00:03:04.819 --> 00:03:07.487 position:16% line:83% align:start
Fairies really kinda live
like shut-ins, you know.

00:03:07.622 --> 00:03:09.322 position:21% line:83% align:start
Didn't I ask that you
not call us "shut-ins?"

00:03:09.456 --> 00:03:10.825 position:33% line:83% align:start
[ADVENTURERS]
Miss Tania!

00:03:10.958 --> 00:03:12.593 position:19% line:89% align:start
Nice to see you again!

00:03:12.727 --> 00:03:14.796 position:7% line:89% align:start
I've beaten you two up before.

00:03:14.929 --> 00:03:15.830 position:35% line:89% align:start
Haven't I?

00:03:15.963 --> 00:03:17.065 position:33% line:83% align:start
[ADVENTURERS]
Yup!

00:03:17.197 --> 00:03:18.398 position:30% line:83% align:start
[ADVENTURER 8B]
On Stride Bridge.

00:03:18.533 --> 00:03:19.701 position:30% line:83% align:start
I gotta admit,
getting wrecked by a girl

00:03:19.834 --> 00:03:21.368 position:19% line:83% align:start
was pretty humiliating
at first, but...

00:03:21.502 --> 00:03:22.970 position:21% line:89% align:start
You're a dragon, so--

00:03:23.104 --> 00:03:24.337 position:21% line:89% align:start
[TANIA, KANADE gasp]

00:03:24.471 --> 00:03:26.007 position:30% line:83% align:start
[ADVENTURER 8A]
Uh, what he means is,

00:03:26.140 --> 00:03:27.709 position:7% line:83% align:start
those bruises and broken bones
are like a badge of honor!

00:03:27.842 --> 00:03:29.242 position:30% line:83% align:start
[ADVENTURER 8B]
We just wanted to let you know

00:03:29.376 --> 00:03:30.878 position:21% line:89% align:start
and pay our respects!

00:03:31.012 --> 00:03:33.447 position:27% line:83% align:start
Well, once you've
sharpened your skills,

00:03:33.581 --> 00:03:36.184 position:19% line:83% align:start
maybe we can arrange to
have another li'l tussle.

00:03:36.316 --> 00:03:37.585 position:33% line:83% align:start
[ADVENTURERS]
We won't let you down!

00:03:37.719 --> 00:03:39.219 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KANADE]
Good morning, ma'am!

00:03:39.352 --> 00:03:42.724 position:7% line:83% align:start
My, my. Aren't you bright-eyed
and bushy-tailed today?

00:03:42.857 --> 00:03:43.825 position:27% line:89% align:start
Here, take this.

00:03:43.958 --> 00:03:46.527 position:27% line:83% align:start
Oh, my goodness!
Are you sure, though?

00:03:46.661 --> 00:03:48.162 position:27% line:83% align:start
[STAND OWNER 8A]
Of course I am!

00:03:48.295 --> 00:03:50.598 position:7% line:83% align:start
It's the least I can do for all
the help you've given me!

00:03:50.732 --> 00:03:52.600 position:27% line:83% align:start
[KANADE chuckles]
That's so sweet!

00:03:52.734 --> 00:03:54.802 position:27% line:83% align:start
How did they both
assimilate so easily?

00:03:54.936 --> 00:03:57.437 position:21% line:83% align:start
Right? I wish we were
as brave as they are.

00:03:57.572 --> 00:03:58.271 position:27% line:89% align:start
[SORA, RUNA gasp]

00:03:58.405 --> 00:04:00.041 position:30% line:89% align:start
[KIDS chuckle]

00:04:00.174 --> 00:04:01.776 position:7% line:89% align:start
What do you want of us, child?

00:04:01.909 --> 00:04:04.478 position:24% line:83% align:start
We're not afraid to
fight kids, so back off!

00:04:04.612 --> 00:04:05.780 position:16% line:89% align:start
Wow, Rein, it looks like

00:04:05.913 --> 00:04:07.715 position:33% line:83% align:start
you picked up
a couple more wives!

00:04:07.849 --> 00:04:08.783 position:33% line:89% align:start
[REIN gasps]

00:04:08.916 --> 00:04:10.250 position:30% line:83% align:start
What's it like
to be Rein's wife?

00:04:10.383 --> 00:04:11.219 position:24% line:83% align:start
I'm afraid you have
the wrong idea--

00:04:11.384 --> 00:04:12.553 position:21% line:89% align:start
we're not his wives!

00:04:12.687 --> 00:04:14.055 position:24% line:83% align:start
That sure made you
blush a lot, huh?

00:04:14.188 --> 00:04:17.525 position:19% line:83% align:start
You two are so pretty!
Are you flower spirits?

00:04:17.658 --> 00:04:21.162 position:19% line:83% align:start
Pretty? Um. Thank you,
human child.

00:04:21.294 --> 00:04:24.198 position:33% line:89% align:start
[RUNA laughs]

00:04:24.331 --> 00:04:27.668 position:10% line:83% align:start
[RUNA] You've got a good eye,
girlie. I'll give you that!

00:04:27.802 --> 00:04:30.638 position:27% line:83% align:start
But mistaking us
for flower spirits?

00:04:30.772 --> 00:04:34.307 position:21% line:83% align:start
Foolish child. Behold
the depth of my sorcery!

00:04:34.441 --> 00:04:35.977 position:35% line:89% align:start
[KIDS gasp]

00:04:36.110 --> 00:04:38.411 position:19% line:83% align:start
[RUNA] I am an ultimate
wielder of magic, a proud fai--

00:04:38.546 --> 00:04:39.847 position:27% line:89% align:start
[SORA, REIN yelp]

00:04:39.981 --> 00:04:42.315 position:19% line:83% align:start
[RUNA] I can't believe
you guys stopped me!

00:04:42.449 --> 00:04:43.584 position:24% line:83% align:start
Those little brats
were practically

00:04:43.718 --> 00:04:45.485 position:16% line:89% align:start
begging me to school 'em!

00:04:45.620 --> 00:04:46.888 position:27% line:83% align:start
You were the one
who said we had to be

00:04:47.021 --> 00:04:48.589 position:24% line:83% align:start
extra careful not
to show the humans

00:04:48.723 --> 00:04:50.423 position:10% line:89% align:start
that we're fairies, remember?

00:04:50.558 --> 00:04:51.993 position:21% line:83% align:start
But as soon as your
pride gets insulted,

00:04:52.126 --> 00:04:54.427 position:27% line:83% align:start
all that goes out
the window, as usual.

00:04:54.562 --> 00:04:55.730 position:30% line:89% align:start
It's all right.

00:04:55.863 --> 00:04:57.364 position:5% line:89% align:start
Getting accustomed to life here

00:04:57.497 --> 00:04:59.967 position:19% line:83% align:start
is gonna take a little
bit of time, is all.

00:05:00.101 --> 00:05:01.903 position:21% line:89% align:start
Uh? Hey, is that it?

00:05:02.036 --> 00:05:04.772 position:10% line:83% align:start
[KANADE] The best weapon shop
in the city, or so they say.

00:05:04.906 --> 00:05:07.407 position:21% line:83% align:start
Nothing but the best
for our fearless leader!

00:05:07.542 --> 00:05:08.743 position:24% line:89% align:start
Let's go shopping!

00:05:08.876 --> 00:05:10.443 position:33% line:89% align:start
[door opens]

00:05:11.179 --> 00:05:12.914 position:41% line:83% align:start
[GANTZ]
What do ya want?

00:05:13.047 --> 00:05:14.649 position:24% line:89% align:start
[RUNA, SORA grunt]

00:05:14.782 --> 00:05:18.619 position:10% line:83% align:start
Problem? You look like you've
never seen a dwarf before.

00:05:18.753 --> 00:05:20.188 position:41% line:83% align:start
[REIN]
Yeah, of course we have.

00:05:20.320 --> 00:05:22.757 position:19% line:83% align:start
We just came in to try
and find some new equipment.

00:05:22.890 --> 00:05:23.925 position:41% line:83% align:start
[GANTZ]
Hurry up, then.

00:05:24.058 --> 00:05:25.458 position:21% line:89% align:start
I don't have all day.

00:05:25.593 --> 00:05:27.394 position:19% line:83% align:start
Mr. Shopkeeper is a bit
intimidating, isn't he?

00:05:27.528 --> 00:05:30.430 position:13% line:83% align:start
Dwarves are kinda notorious
for being cranky little guys.

00:05:30.565 --> 00:05:31.299 position:30% line:89% align:start
[GANTZ growls]

00:05:31.431 --> 00:05:32.332 position:30% line:89% align:start
[KANADE yelps]

00:05:32.465 --> 00:05:33.734 position:13% line:89% align:start
Dwarves are also notorious

00:05:33.868 --> 00:05:36.170 position:24% line:83% align:start
for being the best
blacksmiths in the world.

00:05:36.304 --> 00:05:37.572 position:41% line:83% align:start
[RUNA]
Hey, Rein!

00:05:37.705 --> 00:05:39.140 position:16% line:89% align:start
What about this bad boy?

00:05:39.273 --> 00:05:40.842 position:41% line:83% align:start
[REIN]
A whip?

00:05:40.975 --> 00:05:43.376 position:13% line:83% align:start
Runa, I do not believe that
sort of weapon would suit him.

00:05:43.511 --> 00:05:46.446 position:21% line:83% align:start
Can you just imagine
our "tamer" with it?

00:05:46.581 --> 00:05:49.250 position:16% line:83% align:start
"Do exactly what I say or
I'm gonna give it to ya!"

00:05:49.382 --> 00:05:50.852 position:30% line:89% align:start
[SORA whimpers]

00:05:50.985 --> 00:05:52.520 position:10% line:83% align:start
It'd be great 'cause he could
use it for "other" stuff.

00:05:52.653 --> 00:05:54.789 position:24% line:83% align:start
I'm talkin', like,
unspeakable stuff.

00:05:54.922 --> 00:05:57.558 position:41% line:83% align:start
[SORA]
Unspeakable stuff?

00:05:57.692 --> 00:06:00.795 position:21% line:83% align:start
Stop being so impure!
He'd never do such things!

00:06:00.928 --> 00:06:02.429 position:27% line:83% align:start
Looks like you're
blushing again.

00:06:02.563 --> 00:06:04.532 position:24% line:83% align:start
Are you embarrassed
by your dirty mind?

00:06:04.665 --> 00:06:06.133 position:33% line:83% align:start
[SORA shouts]
Runa!

00:06:06.267 --> 00:06:07.802 position:30% line:89% align:start
[RUNA cackles]

00:06:07.935 --> 00:06:09.770 position:10% line:83% align:start
If you keep hitting me, Rein
might have to whip you, Sis!

00:06:09.904 --> 00:06:13.541 position:16% line:83% align:start
Please get her off of me.
This is really starting to hurt.

00:06:13.674 --> 00:06:15.408 position:41% line:83% align:start
[REIN]
Hey. This one looks good!

00:06:15.543 --> 00:06:17.111 position:41% line:89% align:start
Really?

00:06:17.245 --> 00:06:19.180 position:13% line:83% align:start
Surely you deserve a weapon
with a little more size to it.

00:06:19.313 --> 00:06:21.949 position:19% line:83% align:start
I'm more familiar with
these types of weapons.

00:06:23.217 --> 00:06:25.019 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KANADE]
So pretty!

00:06:25.152 --> 00:06:27.420 position:13% line:83% align:start
[REIN] Hm? Something about
this dagger feels off.

00:06:27.555 --> 00:06:29.323 position:21% line:89% align:start
It looks fine, but...

00:06:29.456 --> 00:06:30.791 position:35% line:89% align:start
Hey there!

00:06:30.925 --> 00:06:33.227 position:21% line:83% align:start
I hear you've got the
best weapon shop in town.

00:06:33.361 --> 00:06:36.429 position:13% line:83% align:start
I'm looking for the finest
weapon that money can buy!

00:06:36.564 --> 00:06:39.600 position:30% line:83% align:start
This should be
enough to cover it.

00:06:39.734 --> 00:06:41.702 position:24% line:89% align:start
Looks like enough.

00:06:44.939 --> 00:06:46.607 position:41% line:83% align:start
[GANTZ]
My finest weapon.

00:06:46.741 --> 00:06:49.476 position:21% line:83% align:start
[CUSTOMER 8A gasps]
This thing is sweet!

00:06:49.610 --> 00:06:51.545 position:24% line:83% align:start
I could wreck some
monsters with this!

00:06:51.679 --> 00:06:52.546 position:24% line:89% align:start
Thanks, little guy!

00:06:52.680 --> 00:06:54.315 position:35% line:89% align:start
Of course.

00:06:54.447 --> 00:06:56.684 position:21% line:89% align:start
[CUSTOMER 8A humming]

00:06:56.817 --> 00:07:00.453 position:16% line:83% align:start
Me-ow! Did you catch how
beautiful that sword is?

00:07:00.588 --> 00:07:02.523 position:33% line:89% align:start
What's wrong?

00:07:02.657 --> 00:07:04.025 position:41% line:83% align:start
[REIN]
Excuse me, sir.

00:07:04.158 --> 00:07:05.927 position:24% line:83% align:start
The sword that you
just sold that guy?

00:07:06.060 --> 00:07:08.296 position:13% line:83% align:start
There's no way that's the
best weapon you have here.

00:07:08.428 --> 00:07:09.797 position:21% line:89% align:start
[TANIA, KANADE gasp]

00:07:09.931 --> 00:07:11.464 position:41% line:83% align:start
[GANTZ]
You callin' me a liar?

00:07:11.599 --> 00:07:13.801 position:16% line:83% align:start
Now, don't get me wrong;
it's a beautiful sword.

00:07:13.935 --> 00:07:15.603 position:21% line:83% align:start
But the way it looks
has nothing to do with

00:07:15.736 --> 00:07:17.538 position:5% line:89% align:start
how well it holds up in combat.

00:07:17.672 --> 00:07:19.173 position:13% line:89% align:start
And it's not just that one.

00:07:19.307 --> 00:07:21.409 position:13% line:83% align:start
I don't think any of these
would last in a real fight.

00:07:21.542 --> 00:07:22.410 position:21% line:89% align:start
[TANIA, KANADE gasp]

00:07:22.543 --> 00:07:24.278 position:41% line:83% align:start
[GANTZ]
Hm.

00:07:24.412 --> 00:07:25.646 position:38% line:89% align:start
I wonder.

00:07:25.780 --> 00:07:27.748 position:5% line:89% align:start
Is any of this your "best" work?

00:07:27.882 --> 00:07:28.649 position:21% line:89% align:start
[TANIA, KANADE grunt]

00:07:28.783 --> 00:07:30.551 position:24% line:89% align:start
[RUNA, SORA grunt]

00:07:30.685 --> 00:07:34.655 position:16% line:89% align:start
[GANTZ chuckles, laughs]

00:07:34.789 --> 00:07:37.124 position:21% line:83% align:start
That's some keen eye
you've got there, kid.

00:07:37.258 --> 00:07:38.793 position:21% line:89% align:start
Ain't no fooling you.

00:07:38.926 --> 00:07:40.394 position:13% line:89% align:start
This is all stuff I whip up

00:07:40.528 --> 00:07:42.029 position:30% line:83% align:start
to make a quick
coin off the guys

00:07:42.163 --> 00:07:45.433 position:7% line:83% align:start
that wouldn't know a good sword
if I stabbed 'em with it.

00:07:45.566 --> 00:07:48.402 position:16% line:83% align:start
So, basically you're just
ripping people off here, huh?

00:07:48.536 --> 00:07:49.837 position:33% line:89% align:start
How shocking.

00:07:49.971 --> 00:07:51.872 position:21% line:83% align:start
I had no idea dwarves
could be so devious.

00:07:52.006 --> 00:07:53.708 position:5% line:89% align:start
Although they may be half-arsed,

00:07:53.841 --> 00:07:56.277 position:10% line:83% align:start
they're still born of actual
Dwarven craftsmanship,

00:07:56.410 --> 00:08:00.114 position:10% line:83% align:start
which makes them worth every
last bit of coin I charge!

00:08:00.247 --> 00:08:01.649 position:33% line:89% align:start
That said...

00:08:04.085 --> 00:08:05.252 position:33% line:89% align:start
[REIN gasps]

00:08:05.386 --> 00:08:06.887 position:21% line:83% align:start
[GANTZ] They're mere
toys compared to these.

00:08:07.021 --> 00:08:10.257 position:27% line:83% align:start
The ones I really
pour my heart into.

00:08:10.391 --> 00:08:13.160 position:10% line:83% align:start
They're even more impressive
than I ever imagined.

00:08:13.294 --> 00:08:15.096 position:30% line:83% align:start
If you can make
weapons this incredible,

00:08:15.229 --> 00:08:17.665 position:21% line:83% align:start
why would you deceive
your customers like that?

00:08:17.798 --> 00:08:19.633 position:33% line:83% align:start
[GANTZ sighs]
I know it's not right,

00:08:19.767 --> 00:08:21.235 position:27% line:83% align:start
but I can't bring
myself to sell these

00:08:21.369 --> 00:08:23.771 position:5% line:89% align:start
to every schmuck with some coin.

00:08:23.904 --> 00:08:25.606 position:24% line:83% align:start
No one cares about
the craftsmanship

00:08:25.740 --> 00:08:27.742 position:21% line:83% align:start
behind what they're
wielding these days.

00:08:27.875 --> 00:08:29.944 position:13% line:83% align:start
They're always just looking
for the next best thing

00:08:30.077 --> 00:08:32.279 position:24% line:83% align:start
they can get their
grubby little paws on.

00:08:32.413 --> 00:08:35.282 position:19% line:83% align:start
And if they do purchase
a weapon I'm truly proud of,

00:08:35.416 --> 00:08:38.252 position:19% line:83% align:start
they toss it aside when
they find something shinier.

00:08:38.386 --> 00:08:42.223 position:19% line:83% align:start
That kind of disrespect
takes a toll on a person.

00:08:42.356 --> 00:08:43.524 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sighs]

00:08:43.657 --> 00:08:45.760 position:30% line:89% align:start
[GANTZ grunts]

00:08:45.893 --> 00:08:47.962 position:13% line:83% align:start
[GANTZ] A true weaponsmith
puts a piece of himself

00:08:48.095 --> 00:08:49.797 position:10% line:89% align:start
inside every weapon he makes.

00:08:49.930 --> 00:08:51.499 position:13% line:89% align:start
They're like his children.

00:08:51.632 --> 00:08:56.604 position:10% line:83% align:start
Is it selfish to want them to
go to someone truly worthy?

00:08:56.737 --> 00:08:58.806 position:24% line:89% align:start
[RUNA, SORA grunt]

00:08:58.939 --> 00:09:00.708 position:30% line:83% align:start
I totally smell
what you're cookin'!

00:09:00.841 --> 00:09:01.776 position:41% line:83% align:start
[GANTZ]
Hm?

00:09:01.909 --> 00:09:03.411 position:10% line:89% align:start
I mean, it just makes sense.

00:09:03.544 --> 00:09:05.613 position:21% line:83% align:start
A high-quality weapon
demands a high-quality wielder!

00:09:05.746 --> 00:09:07.681 position:19% line:89% align:start
Uh! My point, exactly!

00:09:07.815 --> 00:09:09.016 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TANIA]
I'm actually something...

00:09:09.150 --> 00:09:10.785 position:27% line:83% align:start
They're like kith
and kin, aren't they?

00:09:10.918 --> 00:09:13.054 position:10% line:83% align:start
Well, they do have a healthy
self-esteem in common,

00:09:13.187 --> 00:09:14.188 position:35% line:89% align:start
I suppose.

00:09:15.456 --> 00:09:16.390 position:41% line:83% align:start
[GANTZ]
All right.

00:09:16.525 --> 00:09:18.559 position:5% line:89% align:start
I want you to tell me something.

00:09:18.692 --> 00:09:19.894 position:13% line:89% align:start
How did you know that those

00:09:20.027 --> 00:09:22.296 position:27% line:83% align:start
weren't the best
weapons I had to offer?

00:09:22.430 --> 00:09:23.397 position:47% line:89% align:start
Uh?

00:09:23.532 --> 00:09:24.832 position:41% line:83% align:start
[GANTZ]
To the naked eye,

00:09:24.965 --> 00:09:27.168 position:21% line:83% align:start
these are fine enough
to fool almost everyone.

00:09:27.301 --> 00:09:28.669 position:21% line:89% align:start
What tipped you off?

00:09:28.803 --> 00:09:30.805 position:5% line:89% align:start
Honestly, I'm not entirely sure,

00:09:30.938 --> 00:09:33.508 position:27% line:83% align:start
but maybe it has
something to do with the fact

00:09:33.641 --> 00:09:34.642 position:19% line:89% align:start
that I'm a beast tamer?

00:09:34.775 --> 00:09:35.910 position:41% line:83% align:start
[GANTZ]
Oh.

00:09:36.043 --> 00:09:37.711 position:27% line:83% align:start
[REIN] Taming an
animal takes some skill.

00:09:37.845 --> 00:09:39.213 position:10% line:89% align:start
We have to observe it closely

00:09:39.346 --> 00:09:42.049 position:13% line:83% align:start
so we can connect with it,
almost see its soul.

00:09:42.183 --> 00:09:43.518 position:30% line:83% align:start
I must've just
started doing that

00:09:43.651 --> 00:09:44.885 position:13% line:89% align:start
with everything in my life.

00:09:45.019 --> 00:09:47.221 position:33% line:83% align:start
It's kind of
a blessing and a curse.

00:09:47.354 --> 00:09:48.489 position:41% line:89% align:start
I see.

00:09:48.622 --> 00:09:50.024 position:33% line:83% align:start
Perhaps your
vocation is related.

00:09:50.157 --> 00:09:51.859 position:21% line:83% align:start
But Rein isn't your
average beast tamer,

00:09:51.992 --> 00:09:53.327 position:24% line:89% align:start
he's one of a kind.

00:09:53.461 --> 00:09:54.395 position:21% line:89% align:start
He's the cat's meow.

00:09:54.529 --> 00:09:55.996 position:41% line:83% align:start
[REIN]
Hm?

00:09:56.130 --> 00:09:57.631 position:19% line:83% align:start
Hey, guys. What are you
muttering about over there?

00:09:57.765 --> 00:09:59.534 position:30% line:83% align:start
[TANIA, KANADE]
You'll understand someday.

00:09:59.667 --> 00:10:01.570 position:41% line:83% align:start
[RUNA]
You're freaking me out.

00:10:01.702 --> 00:10:03.270 position:41% line:83% align:start
[GANTZ]
I like you, kid!

00:10:03.404 --> 00:10:06.508 position:10% line:83% align:start
And I would be proud to make
a personalized weapon for you!

00:10:06.640 --> 00:10:07.741 position:33% line:89% align:start
Wow, really?

00:10:07.875 --> 00:10:08.976 position:30% line:89% align:start
That's so nice!

00:10:09.110 --> 00:10:10.277 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yeah.

00:10:10.411 --> 00:10:11.879 position:21% line:83% align:start
A high-quality weapon
for a high-quality guy!

00:10:12.012 --> 00:10:13.582 position:7% line:89% align:start
You would be truly unbeatable!

00:10:13.714 --> 00:10:15.049 position:38% line:89% align:start
Our hero!

00:10:15.182 --> 00:10:16.551 position:21% line:83% align:start
[TANIA] Think of all
the big scary things...

00:10:16.684 --> 00:10:19.286 position:27% line:83% align:start
Uh, there's just
one teensy-tiny issue.

00:10:19.420 --> 00:10:20.754 position:44% line:83% align:start
[ALL]
Uh?

00:10:20.888 --> 00:10:24.058 position:19% line:83% align:start
I don't have the right
material to craft one.

00:10:24.191 --> 00:10:25.326 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:10:28.195 --> 00:10:30.431 position:21% line:83% align:start
[REIN] So many people
at the job board today.

00:10:30.565 --> 00:10:33.667 position:21% line:83% align:start
[TANIA] And they seem
excited about something.

00:10:33.801 --> 00:10:35.669 position:30% line:83% align:start
[KANADE gasps]
Hey, Natalie!

00:10:35.803 --> 00:10:37.838 position:30% line:83% align:start
Kanade! So good
to see you, friend.

00:10:37.972 --> 00:10:38.906 position:30% line:89% align:start
Yeah, likewise!

00:10:39.039 --> 00:10:40.708 position:5% line:89% align:start
You wouldn't happen to know why

00:10:40.841 --> 00:10:42.243 position:19% line:83% align:start
everyone's so eager to
pounce today, would you?

00:10:42.376 --> 00:10:43.644 position:19% line:89% align:start
You haven't heard yet?

00:10:43.777 --> 00:10:46.180 position:24% line:83% align:start
The hero's party is
staying in Horizon.

00:10:46.313 --> 00:10:48.782 position:13% line:83% align:start
They're recruiting members
to kill the Demon King!

00:10:48.916 --> 00:10:49.750 position:30% line:89% align:start
[KANADE sighs]

00:10:49.884 --> 00:10:51.620 position:16% line:89% align:start
Not those jerkwads again.

00:10:51.785 --> 00:10:52.686 position:38% line:83% align:start
[NATALIE]
I mean, sure.

00:10:52.820 --> 00:10:54.355 position:10% line:89% align:start
It's just the support party,

00:10:54.488 --> 00:10:56.157 position:10% line:83% align:start
but being a part of the team
that defeats the Demon King,

00:10:56.290 --> 00:10:58.926 position:21% line:83% align:start
that's sure to bring
fame and fortune!

00:11:02.029 --> 00:11:03.397 position:30% line:83% align:start
[KANADE, TANIA]
Rein?

00:11:09.670 --> 00:11:10.938 position:21% line:89% align:start
[KANADE, TANIA gasp]

00:11:11.071 --> 00:11:13.741 position:16% line:83% align:start
I don't care about that.
I have you guys now.

00:11:13.874 --> 00:11:15.910 position:41% line:83% align:start
[BOTH]
All right.

00:11:16.043 --> 00:11:18.580 position:24% line:89% align:start
[RUNA, SORA grunt]

00:11:18.712 --> 00:11:21.448 position:7% line:83% align:start
You haven't introduced us yet.
Who are these cuties?

00:11:21.583 --> 00:11:25.452 position:27% line:83% align:start
Oh, you mean us?
I'm Sora, nice to meet you.

00:11:25.587 --> 00:11:26.754 position:33% line:89% align:start
And I'm Runa!

00:11:26.887 --> 00:11:28.623 position:7% line:89% align:start
What's your name, human woman?

00:11:28.756 --> 00:11:31.025 position:16% line:83% align:start
Well, my name is Natalie,
and I work here.

00:11:31.158 --> 00:11:33.194 position:13% line:89% align:start
Are you friends of Rein's?

00:11:33.327 --> 00:11:34.695 position:38% line:83% align:start
--Kinda.
--Listen.

00:11:34.828 --> 00:11:37.731 position:13% line:83% align:start
Our relationship is so much
deeper than just "friendship."

00:11:37.865 --> 00:11:39.634 position:24% line:83% align:start
He knows us inside
and out and all around.

00:11:39.767 --> 00:11:40.602 position:30% line:89% align:start
[SORA shrieks]

00:11:40.734 --> 00:11:42.036 position:19% line:89% align:start
Rein! Are you serious?

00:11:42.169 --> 00:11:44.805 position:24% line:83% align:start
What are you doing?
They're so young.

00:11:44.939 --> 00:11:46.675 position:24% line:89% align:start
No! Wait! Natalie!

00:11:46.807 --> 00:11:48.275 position:30% line:83% align:start
Uh. This isn't
what it looks like!

00:11:48.409 --> 00:11:51.278 position:10% line:83% align:start
I'll never understand humans,
but they're so funny!

00:11:51.412 --> 00:11:52.681 position:24% line:89% align:start
Don't laugh at him.

00:11:52.813 --> 00:11:54.748 position:13% line:83% align:start
[REIN] Regardless, I'd like
to take this job today.

00:11:54.882 --> 00:11:56.685 position:24% line:89% align:start
If you don't mind.

00:11:56.817 --> 00:11:58.252 position:24% line:89% align:start
Let's take a look.

00:11:58.385 --> 00:12:00.821 position:21% line:83% align:start
I see that this here
is an official request

00:12:00.955 --> 00:12:02.923 position:24% line:83% align:start
"to help locate and
acquire mithril ore

00:12:03.057 --> 00:12:04.291 position:10% line:89% align:start
for the weaponsmith, Gantz."

00:12:04.425 --> 00:12:07.261 position:27% line:83% align:start
It seems he named
you specifically.

00:12:07.394 --> 00:12:08.697 position:41% line:83% align:start
[REIN]
Hm.

00:12:08.829 --> 00:12:11.165 position:19% line:83% align:start
[GANTZ] If I'm to craft
a truly great weapon for you,

00:12:11.298 --> 00:12:13.702 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'm going to need an
ore known as "mithril."

00:12:13.834 --> 00:12:15.402 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KANADE]
Mithril?

00:12:15.537 --> 00:12:17.572 position:10% line:83% align:start
Yes, indeed. The legends say
a weapon crafted from mithril

00:12:17.706 --> 00:12:19.373 position:27% line:83% align:start
is strong enough
to last forever.

00:12:19.507 --> 00:12:22.076 position:7% line:83% align:start
But of course, it's practically
impossible to find.

00:12:22.209 --> 00:12:23.477 position:41% line:83% align:start
[GANTZ]
True.

00:12:23.612 --> 00:12:25.045 position:24% line:83% align:start
But I was fortunate
enough to acquire a mine

00:12:25.179 --> 00:12:26.715 position:21% line:83% align:start
that was passed down
from my ancestors,

00:12:26.847 --> 00:12:29.551 position:13% line:83% align:start
so I've always had a rather
ample supply of it on hand.

00:12:29.684 --> 00:12:30.918 position:30% line:83% align:start
[KANADE, RUNA]
You must be rich!

00:12:31.051 --> 00:12:32.621 position:41% line:83% align:start
[GANTZ]
But recently,

00:12:32.753 --> 00:12:34.755 position:10% line:83% align:start
I haven't been able to find
a scrap in the entire place,

00:12:34.888 --> 00:12:36.290 position:10% line:89% align:start
as if it vanished overnight.

00:12:36.423 --> 00:12:38.259 position:30% line:83% align:start
Is it possible
that you mined it all?

00:12:38.392 --> 00:12:40.595 position:27% line:83% align:start
No. I don't think
that's the case.

00:12:40.729 --> 00:12:42.162 position:5% line:89% align:start
If he'd just exhausted the vein,

00:12:42.296 --> 00:12:44.599 position:24% line:83% align:start
he would have seen
a gradual decline.

00:12:44.733 --> 00:12:48.369 position:19% line:83% align:start
It wouldn't have just
disappeared, you know?

00:12:48.503 --> 00:12:49.970 position:21% line:89% align:start
Oh! That makes sense!

00:12:50.104 --> 00:12:51.205 position:33% line:89% align:start
It's strange.

00:12:51.338 --> 00:12:52.840 position:27% line:83% align:start
Things like that
just don't happen,

00:12:52.973 --> 00:12:54.375 position:21% line:83% align:start
so there must be some
explanation for it.

00:12:54.509 --> 00:12:57.211 position:27% line:83% align:start
I wish I knew why
because as it stands,

00:12:57.344 --> 00:12:59.847 position:5% line:89% align:start
I can't craft my finest weapons.

00:12:59.980 --> 00:13:01.949 position:33% line:89% align:start
My apologies.

00:13:02.082 --> 00:13:03.417 position:41% line:83% align:start
[REIN]
Hmm.

00:13:03.551 --> 00:13:05.019 position:19% line:83% align:start
[TANIA] We already know
what you want to do.

00:13:05.152 --> 00:13:06.420 position:16% line:89% align:start
Just say the word, boss.

00:13:06.554 --> 00:13:08.122 position:13% line:89% align:start
It's written on your face!

00:13:08.255 --> 00:13:10.457 position:21% line:83% align:start
There's no reason to
hold back on our account.

00:13:10.592 --> 00:13:12.893 position:27% line:83% align:start
We are a team and
teams stick together!

00:13:13.027 --> 00:13:15.162 position:21% line:83% align:start
You've got to believe
in all of us, Rein.

00:13:15.296 --> 00:13:19.433 position:27% line:83% align:start
And you've got to
believe in yourself.

00:13:19.567 --> 00:13:21.435 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KANADE]
Mm-hm.

00:13:21.569 --> 00:13:22.803 position:24% line:89% align:start
Then it's settled.

00:13:22.936 --> 00:13:24.639 position:41% line:83% align:start
[GANTZ]
So what's it gonna be, kid?

00:13:24.773 --> 00:13:25.973 position:13% line:89% align:start
If you're open to it, sir,

00:13:26.106 --> 00:13:28.475 position:27% line:83% align:start
we would like to
investigate your mine.

00:13:28.610 --> 00:13:29.744 position:41% line:83% align:start
[GANTZ]
Really?

00:13:29.877 --> 00:13:31.045 position:16% line:89% align:start
It's just so suspicious.

00:13:31.178 --> 00:13:32.547 position:30% line:83% align:start
There's no way
it's a coincidence.

00:13:32.681 --> 00:13:34.982 position:19% line:83% align:start
If we're lucky, we can
find out what happened.

00:13:35.115 --> 00:13:36.383 position:33% line:89% align:start
Maybe ya can.

00:13:36.518 --> 00:13:38.485 position:21% line:83% align:start
But know that danger
might be waiting for you

00:13:38.620 --> 00:13:40.054 position:19% line:89% align:start
every step of the way.

00:13:40.187 --> 00:13:42.923 position:10% line:83% align:start
Danger's just part of the job
for adventurers like us.

00:13:43.057 --> 00:13:43.957 position:30% line:89% align:start
It's all right.

00:13:44.091 --> 00:13:45.426 position:41% line:83% align:start
[GANTZ]
Hmm.

00:13:47.361 --> 00:13:50.497 position:24% line:83% align:start
Perhaps our meeting
is no mere coincidence.

00:13:50.632 --> 00:13:52.966 position:30% line:83% align:start
Very well then,
consider yourselves hired!

00:13:53.100 --> 00:13:54.134 position:30% line:83% align:start
--[GROUP gasps]
--[REIN] Thank you!

00:13:54.268 --> 00:13:56.203 position:13% line:89% align:start
Oh. My name's Rein Shroud.

00:13:56.337 --> 00:13:58.872 position:10% line:89% align:start
A pleasure to meet you, Rein.

00:13:59.006 --> 00:14:01.875 position:24% line:89% align:start
I'm Gantz Stoloff.

00:14:02.009 --> 00:14:03.977 position:27% line:83% align:start
Still gotta iron
out a few things.

00:14:04.111 --> 00:14:05.814 position:27% line:83% align:start
Like exactly how
much gold you'd like

00:14:05.946 --> 00:14:07.549 position:7% line:89% align:start
in exchange for your services.

00:14:07.682 --> 00:14:09.149 position:21% line:89% align:start
[TANIA, KANADE gasp]

00:14:09.283 --> 00:14:11.919 position:13% line:83% align:start
Well, actually, I'd rather
have you make me a weapon.

00:14:12.052 --> 00:14:14.321 position:41% line:83% align:start
[GANTZ]
Oh?

00:14:14.455 --> 00:14:19.694 position:13% line:83% align:start
Really? You covet one of my
precious weapons over gold?

00:14:19.828 --> 00:14:21.895 position:16% line:89% align:start
Why, is that a bad thing?

00:14:22.996 --> 00:14:25.032 position:35% line:89% align:start
Not at all.

00:14:25.165 --> 00:14:27.635 position:16% line:89% align:start
It's the best thing ever!

00:14:29.604 --> 00:14:30.871 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KANADE]
What a surprise.

00:14:31.004 --> 00:14:32.473 position:24% line:83% align:start
At first I thought
Gantz was a sourpuss.

00:14:32.607 --> 00:14:35.476 position:19% line:83% align:start
I mean he is, but he's
also sweet as a kitten!

00:14:35.610 --> 00:14:36.511 position:27% line:89% align:start
Yeah, it's true.

00:14:36.644 --> 00:14:37.846 position:13% line:89% align:start
I want one of his weapons,

00:14:37.978 --> 00:14:39.113 position:24% line:83% align:start
but I want to help
him out even more.

00:14:39.246 --> 00:14:40.147 position:24% line:89% align:start
Come on, you guys!

00:14:40.280 --> 00:14:42.049 position:13% line:89% align:start
Let's do it for ol' Gantz!

00:14:42.182 --> 00:14:43.852 position:41% line:83% align:start
[GROUP]
Yeah!

00:14:43.984 --> 00:14:48.322 position:27% line:89% align:start
[KANADE humming]

00:14:48.455 --> 00:14:50.357 position:16% line:83% align:start
It's great that the mine
is so close to town.

00:14:50.491 --> 00:14:52.827 position:27% line:83% align:start
We barely had to
pack anything at all.

00:14:52.960 --> 00:14:54.495 position:5% line:89% align:start
Purr-fect day for an adventure!

00:14:54.629 --> 00:14:56.997 position:21% line:83% align:start
It almost feels like
we're going for a picnic!

00:14:57.131 --> 00:14:59.567 position:41% line:83% align:start
[REIN]
It's great! Right, guys?

00:14:59.701 --> 00:15:01.636 position:24% line:83% align:start
Looks like they're
struggling a bit.

00:15:01.770 --> 00:15:04.371 position:16% line:83% align:start
Oh, uh, no. Please don't
worry about me, Rein.

00:15:04.506 --> 00:15:06.808 position:30% line:83% align:start
This is great.
I'm really... having fun.

00:15:06.940 --> 00:15:10.177 position:21% line:83% align:start
Why are you trying to
sugarcoat the truth, Sora?

00:15:10.310 --> 00:15:12.580 position:19% line:83% align:start
This is gonna kill me,
and it won't be quick!

00:15:12.714 --> 00:15:14.314 position:21% line:83% align:start
--[RUNA, SORA groan]
--[REIN yelps]

00:15:14.448 --> 00:15:16.116 position:21% line:83% align:start
[REIN] Guys! Please!
Don't let it take you down!

00:15:16.250 --> 00:15:16.950 position:27% line:89% align:start
[RUNA, SORA sigh]

00:15:17.084 --> 00:15:18.686 position:27% line:89% align:start
Sorry about this.

00:15:18.820 --> 00:15:21.890 position:7% line:83% align:start
Fairies are very powerful, but
our stamina is a bit lacking.

00:15:22.022 --> 00:15:24.559 position:24% line:83% align:start
Oh, yeah? It's not
like we could tell.

00:15:24.692 --> 00:15:28.162 position:27% line:83% align:start
Well, it is super
hot and sunny today!

00:15:28.295 --> 00:15:29.263 position:41% line:83% align:start
[REIN]
It's all right.

00:15:29.396 --> 00:15:31.432 position:10% line:89% align:start
Think we're kinda close to...

00:15:32.499 --> 00:15:33.300 position:30% line:89% align:start
[KANADE gasps]

00:15:33.434 --> 00:15:34.702 position:33% line:83% align:start
[RUNA, SORA]
It's a lake!

00:15:34.836 --> 00:15:36.604 position:24% line:89% align:start
Wow! So beautiful!

00:15:36.738 --> 00:15:37.971 position:27% line:89% align:start
And so cold, too!

00:15:38.105 --> 00:15:39.541 position:21% line:83% align:start
How did you know this
was here, Rein?

00:15:39.674 --> 00:15:41.576 position:21% line:83% align:start
Oh, I just spotted it
when I was studying the map.

00:15:41.709 --> 00:15:43.745 position:24% line:83% align:start
