yourself just this once!

00:17:12.099 --> 00:17:13.233 position:33% line:89% align:start
[SORA yelps]

00:17:13.367 --> 00:17:14.434 position:30% line:89% align:start
[SORA grumbles]

00:17:14.569 --> 00:17:18.372 position:41% line:83% align:start
[SORA]
Runa! That's it!

00:17:18.506 --> 00:17:19.774 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KANADE]
I wanna play!

00:17:19.908 --> 00:17:20.742 position:30% line:89% align:start
[KANADE laughs]

00:17:20.875 --> 00:17:22.977 position:27% line:89% align:start
[gasps, whimpers]

00:17:23.110 --> 00:17:24.746 position:27% line:89% align:start
[KANADE screams]

00:17:24.879 --> 00:17:26.681 position:33% line:83% align:start
[REIN gasps]
Kanade?!

00:17:26.814 --> 00:17:28.282 position:24% line:83% align:start
