didn't notice anything?

00:17:28.415 --> 00:17:30.083 position:21% line:89% align:start
I hope they're safe!

00:17:34.154 --> 00:17:38.026 position:33% line:83% align:start
[REIN grunts]
Kanade! What's wrong?

00:17:38.158 --> 00:17:40.160 position:27% line:89% align:start
