00:17:40.294 --> 00:17:42.830 position:27% line:89% align:start
[KANADE whimpers]

00:17:42.964 --> 00:17:43.631 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:17:43.765 --> 00:17:48.570 position:27% line:89% align:start
[ALL stammering]

00:17:51.873 --> 00:17:53.942 position:41% line:83% align:start
[REIN]
Uhh...

00:17:54.074 --> 00:17:54.809 position:41% line:89% align:start
My bad!

00:17:54.943 --> 00:17:57.879 position:27% line:89% align:start
[GROUP whimpers]

00:17:58.012 --> 00:18:00.682 position:30% line:89% align:start
[GROUP screams]

00:18:02.050 --> 00:18:04.919 position:19% line:83% align:start
I'm so sorry. I didn't
mean to see anything.

00:18:05.053 --> 00:18:06.353 position:10% line:89% align:start
I thought you were in danger!

00:18:06.486 --> 00:18:08.056 position:19% line:83% align:start
You gotta pull yourself
together, Sora!

00:18:08.188 --> 00:18:09.089 position:38% line:89% align:start
