00:18:09.222 --> 00:18:10.592 position:41% line:83% align:start
[SORA]
He saw me naked.

00:18:10.725 --> 00:18:12.259 position:19% line:83% align:start
I don't know if she'll
ever recover from this.

00:18:12.392 --> 00:18:15.128 position:24% line:83% align:start
I'll make it up to
you somehow. Please.

00:18:15.262 --> 00:18:16.229 position:27% line:89% align:start
I'll do anything!

00:18:16.363 --> 00:18:18.131 position:30% line:83% align:start
[TANIA, KANADE]
Hm?

00:18:18.265 --> 00:18:20.133 position:38% line:83% align:start
[KANADE]
Anything, you say?

00:18:20.267 --> 00:18:21.669 position:41% line:83% align:start
[TANIA]
Whatever we want?

00:18:21.803 --> 00:18:23.303 position:33% line:89% align:start
Uh. I guess.

00:18:23.437 --> 00:18:25.740 position:10% line:89% align:start
Then I've got a bright idea.

00:18:25.873 --> 00:18:27.140 position:47% line:89% align:start
Uh?

00:18:27.274 --> 00:18:29.109 position:21% line:83% align:start
You're gonna pretend
this didn't happen.

00:18:29.242 --> 00:18:30.812 position:24% line:83% align:start
I mean, it's pretty
embarrassing,

00:18:30.945 --> 00:18:32.046 position:10% line:89% align:start
but it was just an accident.

00:18:32.179 --> 00:18:33.615 position:19% line:89% align:start
You heard me screaming,

00:18:33.748 --> 00:18:35.215 position:13% line:83% align:start
so you just wanted to make
sure we were all right.

00:18:35.349 --> 00:18:36.718 position:24% line:83% align:start
You weren't trying
to sneak a peek.

00:18:36.851 --> 00:18:39.687 position:24% line:83% align:start
It was an accident,
and accidents happen.

00:18:39.821 --> 00:18:40.855 position:41% line:89% align:start
Uh-huh.

00:18:40.989 --> 00:18:43.123 position:24% line:83% align:start
I can't blame you,
so it doesn't bother me.

00:18:43.256 --> 00:18:44.257 position:19% line:89% align:start
I'm still embarrassed,

00:18:44.391 --> 00:18:46.060 position:27% line:83% align:start
and I know it'll
fade eventually.

00:18:46.193 --> 00:18:50.163 position:16% line:83% align:start
But I am hopeful it won't
interfere with our friendship.

00:18:50.297 --> 00:18:51.866 position:33% line:89% align:start
[REIN gasps]

00:18:52.000 --> 00:18:53.367 position:41% line:83% align:start
[REIN]
Thanks, everyone!

00:18:53.500 --> 00:18:55.235 position:24% line:83% align:start
Well, you never got
the chance to go swimming,

00:18:55.369 --> 00:18:57.204 position:24% line:83% align:start
so why don't you go
and take a dip?

00:18:57.337 --> 00:18:58.271 position:41% line:83% align:start
[REIN]
Huh?

00:18:58.405 --> 00:18:59.774 position:13% line:89% align:start
The water feels incredible!

00:18:59.907 --> 00:19:02.309 position:13% line:83% align:start
Maybe we'll "accidentally"
get an eyeful, too!

00:19:02.442 --> 00:19:04.411 position:30% line:89% align:start
See Rein naked?

00:19:04.545 --> 00:19:07.615 position:30% line:83% align:start
[REIN chuckles]
I think I'll pass.

00:19:08.716 --> 00:19:10.785 position:21% line:83% align:start
[REIN] Would you look
at that? We're here!

00:19:10.918 --> 00:19:12.486 position:21% line:83% align:start
Even with our little
detour at the lake,

00:19:12.620 --> 00:19:15.255 position:19% line:83% align:start
we made it to the mine
way ahead of schedule.

00:19:17.157 --> 00:19:20.094 position:19% line:83% align:start
Hey, Rein, shouldn't we
be heading inside already?

00:19:20.227 --> 00:19:22.262 position:19% line:83% align:start
[REIN] I spent the walk
trying to deduce the reason

00:19:22.396 --> 00:19:25.399 position:24% line:83% align:start
