and I've got a theory.

00:19:25.533 --> 00:19:27.869 position:19% line:83% align:start
I think I know what's
going on. It's simple.

00:19:28.002 --> 00:19:28.936 position:21% line:89% align:start
It could be thieves.

00:19:29.070 --> 00:19:30.370 position:30% line:89% align:start
[KANADE gasps]

00:19:30.505 --> 00:19:31.939 position:16% line:83% align:start
So that's why we're just
watching the entrance?

00:19:32.073 --> 00:19:33.675 position:35% line:89% align:start
Of course!

00:19:33.808 --> 00:19:35.543 position:7% line:83% align:start
I bet there are thieves inside,
thieving it up as we speak!

00:19:35.677 --> 00:19:38.445 position:24% line:83% align:start
That is definitely
a real possibility.

00:19:40.581 --> 00:19:42.416 position:41% line:83% align:start
[REIN]
That's peculiar.

00:19:44.351 --> 00:19:45.218 position:33% line:89% align:start
[REIN gasps]

00:19:45.352 --> 00:19:46.453 position:33% line:89% align:start
[GROUP gasps]

00:19:46.587 --> 00:19:47.287 position:41% line:83% align:start
[RUNA]
Hey, don't tell on us!

00:19:47.421 --> 00:19:48.623 position:30% line:89% align:start
Who's out here?

00:19:48.756 --> 00:19:49.691 position:30% line:89% align:start
Show yourself!

00:19:49.824 --> 00:19:50.725 position:38% line:89% align:start
What now?

00:19:50.858 --> 00:19:52.060 position:30% line:83% align:start
[MINE THIEF A]
You can't hide!

00:19:52.192 --> 00:19:53.795 position:21% line:89% align:start
We'll have to fight.

00:19:53.928 --> 00:19:55.897 position:13% line:83% align:start
But I've got some questions
that still need to be answered,

00:19:56.030 --> 00:19:57.131 position:24% line:89% align:start
so go easy on 'em.

00:19:57.264 --> 00:19:58.066 position:30% line:83% align:start
[TANIA, KANADE]
Got it!

00:19:58.198 --> 00:19:59.399 position:21% line:89% align:start
[MINE THIEVES groan]

00:19:59.534 --> 00:20:00.968 position:41% line:83% align:start
[REIN]
Uh.

00:20:01.102 --> 00:20:03.236 position:16% line:83% align:start
Hey, guys, remember when
I told you to go easy on 'em?

00:20:03.370 --> 00:20:04.271 position:41% line:89% align:start
Kinda.

00:20:04.404 --> 00:20:06.007 position:19% line:89% align:start
Well, it's their fault.

00:20:06.140 --> 00:20:08.876 position:7% line:83% align:start
They just decided to run into
my fist as hard as they could!

00:20:09.010 --> 00:20:10.277 position:41% line:83% align:start
[REIN]
Figures.

00:20:10.410 --> 00:20:12.212 position:33% line:83% align:start
No way to get
information from them now.

00:20:12.345 --> 00:20:13.781 position:41% line:83% align:start
[SORA]
If you want,

00:20:13.915 --> 00:20:15.850 position:21% line:83% align:start
