to peer into their memories

00:20:15.983 --> 00:20:17.284 position:13% line:89% align:start
and tell you what we find.

00:20:17.417 --> 00:20:18.953 position:21% line:83% align:start
Huh? You can actually
do that kinda stuff?

00:20:19.087 --> 00:20:21.455 position:21% line:83% align:start
Yes. Our fairy magic
is incredibly powerful,

00:20:21.589 --> 00:20:22.790 position:16% line:89% align:start
don't you remember, Rein?

00:20:22.924 --> 00:20:25.358 position:41% line:83% align:start
[RUNA]
Yeah, we so got this!

00:20:26.493 --> 00:20:28.395 position:24% line:89% align:start
Then let's proceed.

00:20:30.732 --> 00:20:32.734 position:41% line:83% align:start
[BOTH]
Memory Search.

00:20:36.971 --> 00:20:38.573 position:35% line:89% align:start
[ALL gasp]

00:20:48.182 --> 00:20:49.951 position:41% line:83% align:start
[SORA]
You were right!

00:20:50.084 --> 00:20:51.652 position:24% line:83% align:start
I can see multiple
people down there

00:20:51.786 --> 00:20:53.821 position:5% line:89% align:start
