00:20:53.955 --> 00:20:57.525 position:21% line:83% align:start
[RUNA] The two here,
but also, five others.

00:20:57.658 --> 00:20:59.827 position:24% line:83% align:start
And they all appear
to be adventurers.

00:20:59.961 --> 00:21:02.663 position:16% line:83% align:start
It seems the mithral was
being stolen, after all.

00:21:02.797 --> 00:21:05.432 position:21% line:83% align:start
I can't believe these
adventurers would do this.

00:21:05.566 --> 00:21:06.934 position:41% line:83% align:start
[SORA]
Excuse me.

00:21:07.068 --> 00:21:10.505 position:21% line:83% align:start
How'd we do? Were we
able to help out at all?

00:21:10.638 --> 00:21:12.405 position:10% line:89% align:start
Yeah, you most certainly did!

00:21:12.540 --> 00:21:13.574 position:19% line:89% align:start
Thanks a lot, you two!

00:21:13.708 --> 00:21:15.009 position:41% line:83% align:start
[RUNA]
Ooh! Does that mean

00:21:15.143 --> 00:21:17.377 position:19% line:83% align:start
