head pats from you?

00:21:17.512 --> 00:21:18.478 position:33% line:89% align:start
Yes, please!

00:21:18.613 --> 00:21:20.413 position:24% line:89% align:start
Um, some head pats?

00:21:20.548 --> 00:21:22.650 position:21% line:83% align:start
