told us they're wonderful.

00:21:22.784 --> 00:21:24.919 position:21% line:83% align:start
We would really like
to try some, please.

00:21:25.052 --> 00:21:26.821 position:30% line:83% align:start
And you did say
we did a good job,

00:21:26.954 --> 00:21:27.989 position:24% line:89% align:start
so it's only fair.

00:21:28.122 --> 00:21:29.857 position:27% line:83% align:start
