00:21:31.491 --> 00:21:35.328 position:35% line:83% align:start
Good work.
I'm really proud of you two.

00:21:35.462 --> 00:21:37.031 position:33% line:89% align:start
[RUNA gasps]

00:21:37.165 --> 00:21:39.366 position:7% line:83% align:start
[RUNA] This is more incredible
than I could have imagined!

00:21:39.499 --> 00:21:40.535 position:35% line:89% align:start
It's fine.

00:21:40.668 --> 00:21:42.003 position:41% line:83% align:start
[SORA]
My heart is soaring!

00:21:42.136 --> 00:21:43.436 position:41% line:83% align:start
[REIN]
Really?

00:21:44.105 --> 00:21:46.473 position:27% line:83% align:start
[REIN] All right,
are you guys prepared?

00:21:46.607 --> 00:21:47.875 position:24% line:83% align:start
'Cause we're gonna
go into the mine

00:21:48.009 --> 00:21:49.644 position:21% line:89% align:start
and check things out.

00:21:49.777 --> 00:21:52.046 position:16% line:83% align:start
We should probably assume
they know we're here already.

00:21:52.180 --> 00:21:53.413 position:33% line:89% align:start
You're right.

00:21:53.548 --> 00:21:55.616 position:24% line:83% align:start
But how could they
possibly know that?

00:21:55.750 --> 00:21:57.285 position:27% line:83% align:start
Looks they've got
an eye in the sky

00:21:57.417 --> 00:21:58.351 position:19% line:89% align:start
watching us right now.

00:21:58.485 --> 00:22:00.621 position:41% line:83% align:start
[GROUP]
Huh?

00:22:00.755 --> 00:22:02.990 position:21% line:83% align:start
[REIN] The movements
of that bird earlier...

00:22:05.193 --> 00:22:06.861 position:16% line:89% align:start
...lead me to believe...

00:22:07.929 --> 00:22:10.631 position:16% line:83% align:start
[REIN] ...there's a beast
tamer among them.

